# 📝 Todo List V2 (Advanced Version)

A simple but upgraded Todo List application built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
This project focuses on improving DOM manipulation, localStorage handling, and UI structuring.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ➕ Add new tasks
- 💾 Persistent storage using `localStorage`
- 🔁 Data stays after refresh / tab close
- 🧹 Clean and dynamic DOM rendering
- ⚡ Error handling for empty input
- 🎯 Simple and lightweight structure

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)
- Browser LocalStorage API

---

## 📦 How It Works

- User enters a task
- Task is stored in an array
- Array is saved in `localStorage` using JSON
- On page load, data is retrieved and rendered again

---

## 🔧 Core Concept

```javascript
localStorage.setItem("todo", JSON.stringify(todo));
JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("todo"));